title.narrative: Strengthening Pacific Labour Mobility Partnerships (A12860) - Toso Vaka o Manu

description.narrative: This five year (2017-2022) Strengthening Pacific Labour Mobility Activity builds on phase one of the Activity and extends the implementation scope to support growth in the Recognised Seasonal Employer (RSE) scheme, as well as develop new labour mobility initiatives in new sectors and improve delivery and outcomes in the Pacific.
